verses.verse: Rejoice <S%H7442><s%> in the <S%H3068>LORD,<s%> O ye <S%H6662>righteous:<s%> for <S%H8416>praise<s%> is <S%H5000>comely<s%> for the <S%H3477>upright.<s%>

There is <S%H369>no<s%> <S%H4428>king<s%> <S%H3467>saved<s%> by the <S%H7230>multitude<s%> of a <S%H2428>host:<s%> a mighty <S%H1368>man<s%> is <S%H3808>not<s%> <S%H5337>delivered<s%> by <S%H7230>much<s%> <S%H3581>strength.<s%>
A <S%H5483>horse<s%> is a vain <S%H8267>thing<s%> for <S%H8668>safety:<s%> <S%H3808>neither<s%> shall he <S%H4422>deliver<s%> any by his <S%H7230>great<s%> <S%H2428>strength.<s%>

To <S%H5337>deliver<s%> their <S%H5315>soul<s%> from <S%H4480>death,<s%> <S%H4194><s%> and to keep them <S%H2421>alive<s%> in <S%H7458>famine.<s%>
Our <S%H5315>soul<s%> <S%H2442>waiteth<s%> for the <S%H3068>LORD:<s%> <S%H1931>he<s%> is our <S%H5828>help<s%> and our <S%H4043>shield.<s%>
For <S%H3588><s%> our <S%H3820>heart<s%> shall <S%H8055>rejoice<s%> in him, <S%H3588>because<s%> we have <S%H982>trusted<s%> in his <S%H6944>holy<s%> <S%H8034>name.<s%>
